    <h3>Use case 2</h3>
    <h4>UV RADIATION MONITORING</h4>
    <h5>WITH GROUND MEASUREMENTS AND SATELLITE DATA</h5>
    <p>This tutorial demonstrates an example workflow for the currently selected use case.</p>
    <p>It is an interactive tutorial, so you just need to scroll down to see the functionality of the application.</p>
    <p>The tutorial can be closed at any point in time.</p>
